OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist and fog quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave a bright morning
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells. Cloud may tend to
OL,8,Fincrease throughout the afternoon with
OL,9,Fa small risk of the odd light shower.
OL,10,FFeeling warm in the sunshine and light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRather cloudy at times this
OL,14,Fevening with again a small risk of a
OL,15,Fshower. Skies clearing overnight
OL,16,Fallowing it to turn chilly in the
OL,17,Fcountryside by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
